[[Electronic trading|Electronic Trading]] [[communications]] are based on a list of well-defined protocols.
Although [[FIX protocol]] has grown significant [[market share]], the exchange specific protocols (also called "Native" interfaces) have found a strong backing with [[Low latency trading|low latency traders]].
